Definition: nautical) at the ends of the transverse deck beams of a vessel
Example: on her beam-ends means heeled over on the side so that the deck is almost vertical
Synonyms: side, noun, act, navigation, c, nautical, at, the, ends, of, transverse, deck, beams, a, vessel, on, her, means, heeled, over, so, that, is, almost, vertical
Category: noun.location
